      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<h1 class=\"article-title\" id=\"h_01J592EM90T8SB84Z7DB54BSWG\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; font-family: ' Source Sans Pro' , ' Source Serif Pro' , -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, ' Segoe UI' , Roboto, ' Helvetica Neue' , Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 40px; color: #09101d; font-size: 2rem; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\" title=\"Scheduled Maintenance June 29 - 30\">&nbsp;</h1>\n\n<div class=\"article-content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-bottom: 2.5rem; color: #09101d; font-family: ' Source Sans Pro' , ' Source Serif Pro' , -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, ' Segoe UI' , Roboto, ' Helvetica Neue' , Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\n<section class=\"article-body\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block; color: #2a303e;\">\n<p data-sourcepos=\"3:1-3:103\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\">We will be conducting a scheduled maintenance on the Analytics Cloud to switch the nodes that support our services. This upgrade is part of our ongoing efforts to enhance the efficiency of our release process.</p>\n\n<p data-sourcepos=\"5:1-5:19\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">What to Expect:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li><strong>Date:</strong> August 15th, 2024</li>\n\t<li><strong>Downtime:</strong> Approximately 30 minutes</li>\n\t<li><strong>Maintenance Window:</strong> Between 8:00 AM and 8:00 PM PST</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>During this time, you may experience brief interruptions in service. We appreciate your understanding as we work to improve your experience with Analytics Cloud.</p>\n</section>\n</div>"
      },
